TeamMatch: Database Design
Overview

The TeamMatch database is designed to support structured team formation, student data collection, instructor configuration, and analytics tracking. The system ensures data integrity, minimal redundancy, and efficient querying by organizing data into well-defined entities with clear relationships.

This design supports all core system features, including student profile submission, deterministic team generation, contribution tracking, and instructor dashboards.

